On Sunday, 17th of September we have organized a joint excursion on a ship to the Kornati National park, with lunch on the ship, some drinks provided, and various stops at fantastic locations and bays. This excursion is included in the summer school fee. This is a unique adventure, please join us!<br /><br />We need to know well in advance whether you are interested in participating, please let us know by Monday 11th of September...<br /><br />Please do not forget your swimming suit!<br /><br />DC<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><center>
